	        <h1 class="hb">The Mozapolis Solution</h1>
	        <p>Mozapolis uniquely combines elements of social networking and internet technology with traditional entertainment industry components and best practices to create a new media business model with the potential to establish a game-changing and highly lucrative new entertainment industry business paradigm.</p>

