	        <p>Mozapolis is a full service music business that leverages the powerful social networking aspects of an interactive online community in conjunction with all facets of record label operations, including producing and recording, artist management, marketing, promotion and publicity, music publishing, distribution and licensing. Our innovation is applying internet technology and social media networking principles to convert A&R from a primary cost center into a sustainable, profitable revenue generating process.</p>

	        <p>Mozapolis is the only music business entity to monetize artist discovery and development, produce and commercially market music, as well as provide an online resource and community for aspiring musical artists of all types worldwide.</p>
